'''國際滑輪溜冰總會'''（{{lang-en|World Skate}}，{{lang|en|'''WS'''}}）是一個[[國際奧委會|國際奧委會]]認可的[[國際|國際]]性的[[滑輪溜冰|滑輪溜冰]][[體育|體育]]組織。本會是國際輪滑運動總會 (Fédération Internationale de Roller Sports，FIRS) 的繼任者，由FIRS和國際滑板總會會 (ISF) 於2017年9月合併而成，此前FIRS被國際奧委會選為滑板運動的管理機構，為[[2020年夏季奧運會|2020年夏季奧運會]]的滑板賽事做準備<ref>{{Cite web|date=2019-09-30|title=Further steps taken as excitement builds for skateboarding’s Olympic debut at Tokyo 2020|url=https://www.olympic.org/news/further-steps-taken-as-excitement-builds-for-skateboarding-s-olympic-debut-at-tokyo-2020|access-date=2020-10-14|website=International Olympic Committee|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116142000/https://www.olympic.org/news/further-steps-taken-as-excitement-builds-for-skateboarding-s-olympic-debut-at-tokyo-2020}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=Pavitt|first=Michael|date=2017-06-15|title=FIRS and ISF to merge into World Skate to aid development and management of skateboarding|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1051575/firs-and-isf-to-merge-into-world-skate-to-aid-development-and-management-of-skateboarding|url-status=live|access-date=2021-05-01|website=Inside the Games|archive-date=2021-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210726090811/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1051575/firs-and-isf-to-merge-into-world-skate-to-aid-development-and-management-of-skateboarding}}</ref>。

== 總會責任 ==
* 管理法規
* 舉辦國際比賽
* 將滑輪溜冰發展為世界性運動

